Business Brief -- Renaissance Energy Ltd.:
   Firm Plans to Buy Interests
   In Petro-Canada Oil Pools
Mr. Woitas said production from Petro-Canada's interest in
the pools totals 3,000 barrels of oil daily. Renaissance said
the acquisition is expected to close by the end of the month.
   Renaissance and Pancanadian are Calgary-based oil and gas
producers. Petro-Canada, also based in Calgary, is an oil and
gas producer with interests in oil refining and marketing.